      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们来梳理一下基础设施的流量调度流程。入口应该是负载均衡器，然后接到Redis缓存层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以A是负载均衡器，B是Redis。接下来Redis要判断是否需要经过Ingress控制器吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，C节点做成菱形判断框，代表Ingress控制器的决策点。如果不需要Ingress处理，直接走D节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，C画成菱形，分支标No到D。那Yes分支呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Yes分支走到Etcd集群，进行服务发现。然后E后面要再做一个负载均衡的判断F。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "F也是菱形判断框？No分支到G，Yes分支继续往下？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。F的Yes分支要判断Worker节点的可用性，这是H节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "H节点画好了，菱形判断WorkerNode。No分支回到Redis缓存I，Yes分支继续。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
